          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".Analytic form of Maxwellian averaged cross section and",
                ".Data capture cross section obtained by the fit of the",
                " partial cross sections represented by the formula (3)",
                " given in the text, page 187. of ISINN-2,1994 :",
                "! Sigma(E) = (17.0+-0.3)/sqrt(E) + (1.50+-0.11)*sqrt(E)",
                " where E is the center-of-mass energy",
                ".Data for MACS obtained from the fit of the total",
                " capture cross sections and represented by the formula",
                " (6) given in the text, page 188. of ISINN-2,1994 :",
                "! <Sigma(T)> = (17.0+-0.3) + (2.25+-0.17)*KT)*/sqrt(KT)"
              ]
            }
          ],
